race.comment: SNAPSHOT (14) is a Holler filly out of Shutter Bug, making her debut here after winning a recent trial at Tatura. Use the market as your best guide. FORTE CHEVAL (1) finished runner-up last start over 1175m at this track, beaten by less than a length. He should improve further and looks a definite each-way hope. EXPLOSIVE STYLE (5) is a 6-year-old mare making her debut, so she must have been worth waiting for. Her trial form is good, and with some luck from a wide gate, she can figure in the finish. SHOWTIME KISTENA (8) has been a consistent maiden and will be a lot stronger after her spell. A wide gate is against her, but she should still be included in all combinations.
